    <content>&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Hello, community!&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;I am encountering an issue while working with an SAP CAP-based application. Despite my best efforts to debug, I haven’t been able to resolve it. I'm sharing the details here, hoping someone can guide me toward a solution.&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;H3 id="toc-hId-1207581271"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Error Details&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/H3&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;The error message I’m facing is as follows:&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-center" image-alt="Error.png" style="width: 675px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/206811iBE1FFED1039B7C71/image-size/large?v=v2&amp;amp;px=999" role="button" title="Error.png" alt="Error.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;H3 id="toc-hId-1011067766"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Context&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/H3&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;I’m working on a CAP application where I need to integrate with an external OData v2 service hosted on SAP SuccessFactors (SFSF). The connection is configured to use an SAP BTP destination. I’m relying on the &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/1862993"&gt;@SAP&lt;/a&gt;/cds&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt; framework to handle the OData service requests.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;H4 id="toc-hId-943636980"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Package.json Configuration&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/H4&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Here's the relevant portion of my &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;package.json&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;:&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-center" image-alt="Package.json.png" style="width: 791px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/206813iFEC58A262781AE68/image-size/large?v=v2&amp;amp;px=999" role="button" title="Package.json.png" alt="Package.json.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;H4 id="toc-hId-747123475"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Connection Handler Code&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/H4&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;This is the function I’m using to connect to the backend:&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-center" image-alt="Custom Handler" style="width: 999px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/206814iF794F4B1F725EB21/image-size/large?v=v2&amp;amp;px=999" role="button" title="CustomHandler.png" alt="Custom Handler" /&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-caption" onclick="event.preventDefault();"&gt;Custom Handler&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;H4 id="toc-hId-550609970"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Service Implementation:&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-center" image-alt="Service.cds" style="width: 705px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/206819iC371C31EDC1AC27F/image-size/large?v=v2&amp;amp;px=999" role="button" title="Service.cds.png" alt="Service.cds" /&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-caption" onclick="event.preventDefault();"&gt;Service.cds&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/H4&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;H3 id="toc-hId-225013746"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Service Handler:&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-center" image-alt="ServiceJs.png" style="width: 642px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/206820iFA80C9A5B4CE7436/image-size/large?v=v2&amp;amp;px=999" role="button" title="ServiceJs.png" alt="ServiceJs.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/H3&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;H2 id="toc-hId--100582478"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Troubleshooting Steps Tried&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/H2&gt;&lt;OL&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Verified all required dependencies and their versions.&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Configured the destination correctly in SAP BTP with valid URL, username, and password.&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Added forwardAuthToken: true to package.json under the credentials for SFSF.&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Ensured the model path is correctly mapped.&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Checked network connectivity and ensured no firewalls are blocking requests.&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/OL&gt;&lt;H4 id="toc-hId--38930545"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-center" image-alt="Destination Setup.png" style="width: 999px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/206824iAFF6BBC1A2893D0F/image-size/large?v=v2&amp;amp;px=999" role="button" title="Destination Setup.png" alt="Destination Setup.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/H4&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;H4 id="toc-hId--235444050"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-center" image-alt="Connection check.png" style="width: 663px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/206825iC48F0B0023B87C8A/image-size/large?v=v2&amp;amp;px=999" role="button" title="Connection check.png" alt="Connection check.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/H4&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;H2 id="toc-hId--690122993"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Question to the Community&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/H2&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Despite implementing these steps, I continue to encounter the error "Error: Error during request to remote service: Failed to build headers." Could someone with experience in CAP-SuccessFactors integration share insights or steps I might have missed?&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;If you've faced and resolved a similar issue or have expertise in this area, I would be grateful for your guidance. Please share your thoughts in the comments below.&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;Thank you in advance for your support!&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/c-khhcw49343/SAP+Community/pd-p/486157991894093153608181816584982" class="lia-product-mention" data-product="1161-1"&gt;SAP Community&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/c-khhcw49343/SAP+TechEd/pd-p/755421404636447943131706525840948" class="lia-product-mention" data-product="268-1"&gt;SAP TechEd&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp; &lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/c-khhcw49343/SAP+BTP+cockpit/pd-p/e6ab964e-18d4-49a1-b26b-46827aa6ca66" class="lia-product-mention" data-product="1245-1"&gt;SAP BTP cockpit&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/c-khhcw49343/SAP+Cloud+Application+Programming+Model/pd-p/9f13aee1-834c-4105-8e43-ee442775e5ce" class="lia-product-mention" data-product="100-1"&gt;SAP Cloud Application Programming Model&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;, &lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/c-khhcw49343/Node.js/pd-p/723714486627645412834578565527550" class="lia-product-mention" data-product="322-1"&gt;Node.js&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/c-khhcw49343/API/pd-p/b31da0dd-f79a-4a1e-988c-af0755c2d184" class="lia-product-mention" data-product="123-1"&gt;API&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/c-khhcw49343/SAP+SuccessFactors+Learning/pd-p/67837800100800006334" class="lia-product-mention" data-product="164-1"&gt;SAP SuccessFactors Learning&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
